      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="33530321">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/54280629/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u54280629-13.jpg" alt="卿云" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33530321/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33530321/" class="">第32页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/54280629/" class=" " title="卿云">卿云</a>
                (The only way out is UP !)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="33530321">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">耐心，耐心，时间是不能吝啬的，只要是向着一个目标在移动，速率自会在时间里增加。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-11-26 19:00</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                耐心，耐心，时间是不能吝啬的，只要是向着一个目标在移动，速率自会在时间里增加。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







